//MPC5534 Register Memory Map Script
//Creates labels for all internal registers from Appendix A of the Reference Manual
//All registers are prefixed with REG_ for easy identification
//@author Generated by claude.ai from MPC5534RM.pdf
//@category MPC55xx
//@keybinding
//@menupath
